<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''脊柱裂'''（{{lang|la|Spina bifida}}）為一種{{tsl|en|neural tube defect|神經管發育缺陷|}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/ntds/Pages/default.aspx |title=Neural Tube Defects (NTDs): Overview |access-date=2015-05-08 |date=2012-11-30 |language=en |archive-date=2015-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509075049/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/ntds/Pages/default.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。乃描述一種[[椎骨|脊椎骨]]及神經管未順利閉合[[先天性障碍|先天性障碍]]<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Over/> -->。主要可分為三類：'''隱性脊柱裂'''（spina bifida occulta）、'''脊髓膜膨出'''（meningocele），以及'''脊髓脊膜膨出'''（myelomeningocele）等三類<ref name=NIH2012Over>{{cite web|title=Spina Bifida: Condition Information|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|date=2012-11-30|accessdate=2017-07-03|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518075105/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最常發生的位置發生於下[[背|背]]部，但也有少數病例發生於頸部及中背部<ref>{{cite book|last1=Deming|first1=Laura|title=Pediatric life care planning and case management|date=2011|publisher=CRC Press|location=Boca Raton, FL|isbn=9781439803585|page=392|edition=2nd|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=XHdTydOXpuoC&pg=PA392|access-date=2017-07-03|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305041700/https://books.google.ca/books?id=XHdTydOXpuoC&pg=PA392|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隱性脊柱裂通常只有輕微症狀，甚至沒有症狀<ref name=NIH2012Diag/>。症狀包含椎間局部有毛、凹窩、暗斑，或腫脹<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Over/> -->。脊髓膜膨出造成的問題不大，椎間可能會出現含液體的囊狀構造<ref name=NIH2012Over/>。脊髓脊髓膜膨出又稱為開放性脊柱裂（open spina bifida），為最嚴重的一型<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->。常見症狀包含走路障礙，膀胱或腸道控制、[[腦積水|腦水腫]]、[[骨髓栓系綜合徵|骨髓栓系綜合徵]]，以及[[乳膠過敏|乳膠過敏]]。認知障礙則較為罕見<ref name=NIH2012Sym>{{cite web|title=Are there disorders or conditions associated with spina bifida?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/disorders-conditions.aspx|accessdate=8 May 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518075103/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/disorders-conditions.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
造成原因可能包含遺傳因素及環境因素<ref name="NIH2012Ca" />。若父母其中有一人，或已有一子罹有脊柱裂，則有4%的機率另一子也會得到該疾病<ref name="NIH2012Epi">{{cite web |title=How many people are affected by or at risk for spina bifida? |url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/affected-risk.aspx |access-date=2015-05-08 |date=2012-11-30 |language=en |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518074316/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/affected-risk.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[妊娠|妊娠]]期間攝取[[葉酸|葉酸]]量不足可能在造成脊柱裂方面扮演重要角色<ref name="NIH2012Ca">{{cite web |title=What causes spina bifida? |url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/causes.aspx |access-date=2015-05-08 |date=2012-11-30 |language=en |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518073039/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/causes.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他風險因子還包含母親服用某些抗癲癇藥物、肥胖，以及[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]控制不佳等等<ref name="NIH2012Epi" />。分娩前後都有機會可以診斷該疾病<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Diag/> -->。出生前的篩檢包含[[羊膜穿刺術|羊膜穿刺]]及超音波，若羊水中含有高含量的[[α-胎兒蛋白|α-胎兒蛋白]] （AFP），則脊柱裂的機會越高<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Diag/> -->。超音波檢測也有機會發現脊柱裂。出生後可用[[醫學影像|影像學]]來確認診斷<ref name="NIH2012Diag">{{cite web|title=How do health care providers diagnose spina bifida?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnose.aspx|accessdate=8 May 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518074318/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnose.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!--Prevention and treatment  -->
大多數脊柱裂可藉由母體妊娠期間充分攝取[[葉酸|葉酸]]來避免<ref name=NIH2012Ca/>，研究證實在[[麵粉|麵粉]]中添加葉酸對大多數婦女有效<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Castillo-Lancellotti|first1=C|last2=Tur|first2=JA|last3=Uauy|first3=R|title=Impact of folic acid fortification of flour on neural tube defects: a systematic review.|journal=Public Health Nutrition|date=May 2013|volume=16|issue=5|pages=901–11|pmid=22850218|doi=10.1017/s1368980012003576}}</ref>。開放性脊柱裂則能在出生後動手術來治療<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx/> -->。若發生腦水腫則建議進行[[引流|引流]]，骨髓栓系綜合徵則可藉由手術修補<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx/> -->。若產生動作障礙可以訂製拐杖及輪椅等輔具改善生活品質<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx/> -->，另外也可能會需要[[导尿|导尿]]<ref name="NIH2012Tx">{{cite web |title=What are the treatments for spina bifida & related conditions? |url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/treatment.aspx |access-date=2015-05-08 |date=2012-11-30 |language=en |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518075220/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/spinabifida/conditioninfo/Pages/treatment.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

<!-- Epidemiology -->
約5%的人有隱性脊柱裂<ref name=ReferenceA>{{cite journal|last1=Sandler|first1=AD|title=Children with spina bifida: key clinical issues.|journal=Pediatric Clinics of North America|date=August 2010|volume=57|issue=4|pages=879–92|pmid=20883878|doi=10.1016/j.pcl.2010.07.009}}</ref>，其他型則隨區域而異，占出生率萬分之一到千分之五不等<ref name=Springer>{{cite book|author1=M. Memet Ö̈zek|title=Spina bifida : management and outcome|date=2008|publisher=Springer|location=Milan|isbn=9788847006508|page=58|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=cpJcUNVgZGMC&pg=PA58|access-date=2017-07-03|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305030951/https://books.google.ca/books?id=cpJcUNVgZGMC&pg=PA58|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]平均約為萬分之四<ref name=ReferenceB>{{cite journal|last1=Kondo|first1=A|last2=Kamihira|first2=O|last3=Ozawa|first3=H|title=Neural tube defects: prevalence, etiology and prevention.|journal=International Journal of Urology |date=January 2009|volume=16|issue=1|pages=49–57|pmid=19120526|doi=10.1111/j.1442-2042.2008.02163.x}}</ref>，跟美國差不多<ref name=NIH2012Epi/><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Canfield|first1=MA|last2=Honein|first2=MA|last3=Yuskiv|first3=N|last4=Xing|first4=J|last5=Mai|first5=CT|last6=Collins|first6=JS|last7=Devine|first7=O|last8=Petrini|first8=J|last9=Ramadhani|first9=TA|last10=Hobbs|first10=CA|last11=Kirby|first11=RS|title=National estimates and race/ethnic-specific variation of selected birth defects in the United States, 1999–2001.|journal=Birth defects research. Part A, Clinical and molecular teratology|date=November 2006|volume=76|issue=11|pages=747–56|pmid=17051527|doi=10.1002/bdra.20294}}</ref>。印度則約每1000名出生孩童中占1.9<ref name="ReferenceC">{{cite journal|last1=Bhide|first1=P|last2=Sagoo|first2=GS|last3=Moorthie|first3=S|last4=Burton|first4=H|last5=Kar|first5=A|title=Systematic review of birth prevalence of neural tube defects in India.|journal=Birth Defects Research. Part A, Clinical and Molecular Teratology|date=July 2013|volume=97|issue=7|pages=437–43|pmid=23873811|doi=10.1002/bdra.23153}}</ref>。族群也可能有所影響，如[[高加索人種|高加索人]]的風險較高，但這可能也與環境因子相關<ref name="Newborn surgery">{{cite book|last1=Puri|first1=Prem|title=Newborn surgery|date=2011|publisher=Hodder Arnold|location=London|isbn=9781444149494|page=811|edition=3|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=TSvSBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA811|access-date=2017-07-03|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305022327/https://books.google.ca/books?id=TSvSBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA811|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
